<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س ل س:</span> شَيْءٌ <span class="c2">(سَلِسٌ)</span> أَيْ سَهْلٌ. وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(سَلِسٌ)</span> أَيْ لَيِّنٌ مُنْقَادٌ بَيِّنُ <span class="c2">(السَّلَسِ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(السَّلَاسَةِ)</span> . وَفُلَانٌ <span class="c2">(سَلِسُ)</span> الْبَوْلِ إِذَا كَانَ لَا يَسْتَمْسِكُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>